        <section class="panel about-panel">
            <h2>About the Deaf Ministry</h2>
            <img src="Images/sign-language.jpg" alt="Sign Language Interpreters">
            <ul>
                <li>Sign language interpretation during services</li>
                <li>Special Bible study sessions tailored for the deaf</li>
                <li>Fellowship events and outreach programs</li>
                <li>Support and counseling for deaf members and visitors</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Why a Deaf Ministry?</h3>
            <p>
                Because everyone deserves to hear the good news of Jesus Christ. This ministry ensures that deaf and hard-of-hearing persons are embraced as vital members of our church family.
            </p>
        </section>

